          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes — Bosch 800 Series and Benchmark refrigerators carry a 5-year limited warranty on the compressor (beyond the 1-year full coverage). Years 2-5: the compressor part itself is covered by Bosch at no cost to you, but labor is your responsibility. This matters because compressor replacement labor runs $380-$580 on these units — instead of paying $680-$1,280 total for a compressor out-of-warranty, you pay $380-$580 labor only during years 2-5. We verify warranty applicability before any major compressor work, process the Bosch warranty claim for the part, and only charge for labor. Bring your original receipt or proof of purchase date — Bosch requires this to process the part claim. Call Bosch customer service at 1-800-944-2904 to confirm your specific model's warranty terms before we schedule."
